trans-unit.source: Represents a dictionary of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsResource" /> elements that are usable across pages of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa um dicionário de elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsResource" /> que podem ser usados nas páginas do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument" />.

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructor.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não tem construtor público.

trans-unit.source: Get a reference to an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsResourceDictionary> by using the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageWriter.AddResourceDictionary%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
trans-unit.target: Obter uma referência a um <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsResourceDictionary> usando o <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageWriter.AddResourceDictionary%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `ResourceDictionary` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 7 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o `ResourceDictionary` elemento de um [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] do pacote, consulte o capítulo 7 a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] especificação, que pode ser obtido em [XPS: especificação e Downloads de licença](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
